latestIgtvVideos.title: Glass Look Makeup ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
These are the steps i follow to achieve a glass look makeup, and this routine has quite literally changed my makeup game.

My makeup always looked cake-y and i hated applying foundation for the same reason.

But prepping your skin before makeup helps the makeup sit so well.
The @nykaabeauty Skin Portion oil and Embryolisse cream (or any moisturiser) has changed my makeup game.

Even after having super dry skin, my makeup shines throughout the day.

Finally filmed the most requested IGTV😛, do let me know if you find this helpful.🥰❤️

#makeup #motd #glasslook #explore
